'''Tsamaiso''' e ka kaya: 

== Kgwebo ==
* Botsamaisi ba kgwebo, tsamaiso ya kgwebo <br>
* Tsamaiso,  mokgwa wa go lebisa batho go ya phitlhelelong ya maikemisitso <br>
* Academic administration, kala ya lefelo la go ithuta (sekao: sekolo) e e lokaganyang le go tlhokomedisa go re e dira jang.  <br>
* Central Administration, ke lefapha tsamaiso je le kwa godimodimo la bodirelo. <br>

== Mmuso/Puso ==
* Kala ya  executive branch ya mmuso kwa tlase ga tlhogo e e rileng ya puso [head of government].
* Public administration, ke mokgwa wa  go tsamaisa [public policy] go ya ka ikemisetso ya mmuso. <br>

== Sengwe ==
* Drug administration, go fa kgotsa naya mothomongwe molemo. <br>
* Military administration, ditegeniki le ditsela tse di dirisiwang ke ditirelo tsa sesole tseo di amanang le tsamaiso ya batlhapetsi ba ntwa. <br>

